INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:
Test::More >= 0.7,
Module::Build >= 0.2808,
Test::Pod >=  1.26,
Test::Pod::Coverage >=  0.55,
CGI::QuickApp >= 0.25,


